citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:32:12.000Z","msg":"不被捕不受傷下次見<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b73f4b89dec025c7269740ee105a0a6da34575","tid":1677967,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:34:11.000Z","msg":"遍地開花前提應該係癱瘓交通<br />\n分區人少，交通冇癱瘓嘅話幾架狗車鏟埋嚟就清晒場<br />\n10月13號就係例子"},{"pid":"7e43d9da9be1f901eb3c0708941787369d619ec8","tid":1677967,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23b73f4b89dec025c7269740ee105a0a6da34575","tid":1677967,"uid":108502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:34:11.000Z","msg":"遍地開花前提應該係癱瘓交通<br />\n分區人少，交通冇癱瘓嘅話幾架狗車鏟埋嚟就清晒場<br />\n10月13號就係例子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:50:21.000Z","msg":"遍地都只係一個小願望<br />\n但係保持住團火先係最緊要<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ef4cb2c6e0dffccadbd19b29e12991500525ec","tid":1677967,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T12:55:29.000Z","msg":"再推幾下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013ef621fee0f7de7d5ef9c0b7a5cca6cefbafc8","tid":1677967,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:01:54.000Z","msg":"睇黎唔係好受歡迎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f1bfebc5089b8a70ac99176ec854808efc22c4","tid":1677967,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T13:09:27.000Z","msg":"再推多野就算<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}